WEBVTT

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:03.020
Injili ya mashaka haikuombi
kua uache kuamini,

00:16:03.737 --> 00:16:05.657
inaomba kua uamini kitu kipya:

00:16:06.200 --> 00:16:08.737
ambacho kinawezekana kutokuamini.

00:16:09.512 --> 00:16:11.682
Inawezekana majibu tuliyonayo
yamekosewa.

00:16:11.706 --> 00:16:14.289
Inawezekana maswali
yenyewe yamekosewa.

00:16:14.313 --> 00:16:18.135
Ndio, injili ya mashaka inamaanisha
kua inawezekana kua sisi,

00:16:18.619 --> 00:16:20.745
kwenye jukwaa hili, kwenye chumba hiki,

00:16:21.178 --> 00:16:22.335
tumekosea.

00:16:22.779 --> 00:16:25.044
Kwa sababu inaleta swali, "Kwanini?"

00:16:25.789 --> 00:16:28.964
Na nguvu zote
tulizonazo mikononi mwetu,

00:16:28.988 --> 00:16:32.368
kwanini watu bado wanateseka vibaya sana?